Code.Terraform:
```hcl
# Enable HSTS with includeSubDomains directive
resource "cloudflare_zone_settings_override" "hsts_subdomains" {
  zone_id = "<ZONE_ID>"
  settings {
    security_header {
      enabled            = true
      include_subdomains = true  # Critical: extends HSTS protection to all subdomains
      max_age            = 31536000
    }
  }
}
```
